---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="AI 競品分析 Dashboard — Case Study | AI PM INSIDER" description="AI 驅動的即時競品分析儀表板，將競品分析時間從 4 小時縮短至 30 分鐘。">

<!-- Hero: 大標題 + 數字並排 -->
<section class="bg-white pt-28 md:pt-36 pb-16 md:pb-20">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <a href="/#portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-body text-brand-subtle hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors mb-8 no-underline">
      <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-left-linear" class="text-lg"></iconify-icon>
      返回作品集
    </a>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-800">Product Sense</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-700">AI Dashboard</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-slate-200 text-slate-700">PM & Builder</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-heading font-black text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-brand-text leading-tight mb-6">
      AI 競品分析<span class="text-brand-accent"> Dashboard</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- 三大數字 -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6 max-w-2xl">
      <div class="text-center py-6 md:py-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-gray-100">
        <div class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl text-brand-accent">8x</div>
        <div class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-brand-subtle mt-1">效率提升</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center py-6 md:py-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-gray-100">
        <div class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl text-brand-text">30<span class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">m</span></div>
        <div class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-brand-subtle mt-1">完成分析</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center py-6 md:py-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-gray-100">
        <div class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl text-emerald-600">即時</div>
        <div class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-brand-subtle mt-1">數據更新</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Problem → Solution：左右對照 -->
<section class="bg-[#F9FAFB] py-16 md:py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="site-container px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:close-circle-bold" class="text-lg text-red-500"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="font-heading font-bold text-red-500 text-sm">Before</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#x2717;</span>手動打開十幾個分頁查競品</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#x2717;</span>資料散落 Notion、Sheets、截圖</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#x2717;</span>整份分析要花半天以上</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#x2717;</span>上週做的分析這週就過期了</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-bold" class="text-lg text-emerald-600"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="font-heading font-bold text-emerald-600 text-sm">After</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">&#x2713;</span>輸入自然語言，AI 即時產出分析</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">&#x2713;</span>一個 Dashboard 集中所有競品資料</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">&#x2713;</span>30 分鐘完成，含比較表格和摘要</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">&#x2713;</span>每日自動追蹤，有變動主動通知</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 架構：橫向流程 -->
<section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="site-container px-6">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-3xl text-brand-text mb-8 text-center">How It Works</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:database-bold" class="text-2xl text-slate-600"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">資料源</p>
        <p class="font-body text-[11px] text-brand-subtle">官網 / G2 / PH</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:filter-bold" class="text-2xl text-blue-600"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">爬取 + 結構化</p>
        <p class="font-body text-[11px] text-brand-subtle">BeautifulSoup</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:magic-stick-3-bold" class="text-2xl text-purple-600"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">AI 分析</p>
        <p class="font-body text-[11px] text-brand-subtle">Gemini AI</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:chart-2-bold" class="text-2xl text-brand-accent"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">Dashboard</p>
        <p class="font-body text-[11px] text-brand-subtle">Streamlit</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 連接箭頭 (desktop) -->
    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center items-center gap-0 max-w-3xl mx-auto -mt-[4.5rem] mb-12 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="flex-1"></div>
      <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-right-linear" class="text-xl text-gray-300"></iconify-icon>
      <div class="flex-1"></div>
      <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-right-linear" class="text-xl text-gray-300"></iconify-icon>
      <div class="flex-1"></div>
      <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-right-linear" class="text-xl text-gray-300"></iconify-icon>
      <div class="flex-1"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 核心功能：icon grid，不是段落 -->
<section class="bg-[#F9FAFB] py-16 md:py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="site-container px-6">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-3xl text-brand-text mb-8 text-center">Core Features</h2>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:chat-round-dots-bold" class="text-3xl text-brand-accent mb-3"></iconify-icon>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">自然語言查詢</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-brand-subtle">用問的就能得到分析</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:radar-2-bold" class="text-3xl text-purple-600 mb-3"></iconify-icon>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">自動追蹤</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-brand-subtle">每日更新競品動態</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:document-text-bold" class="text-3xl text-amber-500 mb-3"></iconify-icon>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">比較報告</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-brand-subtle">一鍵生成多維度表格</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:bell-bing-bold" class="text-3xl text-emerald-500 mb-3"></iconify-icon>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-1">趨勢警報</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-brand-subtle">重大變動即時通知</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 關鍵決策：簡潔版 -->
<section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="site-container px-6">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-3xl text-brand-text mb-8 text-center">Key Decisions</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5">
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-2">Why Streamlit?</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">快速原型驗證優先。PM 團隊可以自己修改，不依賴工程資源。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5">
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-2">Why Gemini?</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">100K+ token 長上下文，一次處理完整資訊。成本比 GPT-4 低，適合高頻場景。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5">
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-brand-text mb-2">Prompt 策略</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">Role + Dimensions + Format 框架，確保每次輸出一致且可操作。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tech Stack + Learnings 合併 -->
<section class="bg-[#F9FAFB] py-16 md:py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="site-container px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Tech Stack -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-brand-text mb-4">Tech Stack</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-blue-700">Python</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-red-600">Streamlit</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-purple-700">Gemini AI</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-green-700">BeautifulSoup</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-emerald-700">Supabase</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Key Learnings -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-brand-text mb-4">Key Learnings</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-accent font-bold">1.</span>PM 也能是 Builder，不需要等工程資源</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-accent font-bold">2.</span>40% 時間花在數據清洗，AI 模型不是瓶頸</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-accent font-bold">3.</span>用戶要的不是「搜尋」而是「追蹤」</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="site-container px-6 text-center">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/#portfolio" class="mag-btn px-6 py-3 border border-brand-light-border text-brand-text font-heading font-medium rounded-full text-sm hover:border-brand-accent hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors no-underline">
        <span>查看更多作品</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/#contact" class="mag-btn px-6 py-3 gold-gradient text-white font-heading font-semibold rounded-full text-sm no-underline">
        <span>與我聯繫</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
